column13: Went out on boat could not change all temperatures, changed in the evening
FLOW STOPPED IN HEADER HOT BUCKET. TEMPERATURE SHOT UP. ADJUSTED TEMPERATURES IN THE AFTERNOON ONCE HOT BUCKET WAS BACK TO TEMPERATURE.
FLOW STOPPED AND CAUSED HEATER TO BURN HOLE THROUGH BUCKET. GOT NEW HEATER AND BUCKET.
UPPED FLOW AFTER CHECKING TO ENSURE TEMPERATURES STAY HIGH.
